  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/a447d631317ce4e6aa1a66f326f2f6c1.avif?t=1735721468\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Three lives, one death. You die — you start over. <br>Items and enemies are different — the dungeon changed…<br>Saved some gold? <br>Great — maybe you’ll live a little longer in the next run.<br><br><strong>This is Carrot Heart — a coop roguelike for 2 players. <br>And you’ll need the second one.</strong><br><br><strong>Why?</strong><br><br>The enemies — 18 types — each with their own abilities. <br>13 of them with 3 armor modifications. <br><br><strong>One enemy — you use one tactic. 3 enemies together — 6 tactics simultaneously. <br>Still want to fight alone?</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/fc78b43b454957ea98fbded9c8ba41e7.poster.avif?t=1735721468\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/fc78b43b454957ea98fbded9c8ba41e7.webm?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/fc78b43b454957ea98fbded9c8ba41e7.mp4?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Use the same weapon all the time — die within a minute. </strong><br><br>12 melee weapons — 7 ranged. <br>Select them according to the situation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/ffa8c3da1a33ed6ccd3b4bdc3a8b5a12.poster.avif?t=1735721468\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/ffa8c3da1a33ed6ccd3b4bdc3a8b5a12.webm?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/ffa8c3da1a33ed6ccd3b4bdc3a8b5a12.mp4?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Weapons break, however… <br>So you use the environment! </strong><br><br>You break that cask with oil — the enemy slows down. <br>You don’t wait —  you burn the oil…<br>…and enjoy the fireshow!<br><br>A fire enemy nearby? Are they fireproof?<br>Break the cask with water and cool ‘em down!  Then immediately electrify them… <br><br><strong>Anything else? </strong><br>Keep an eye on casks with acid, gunpowder, bonfires, and spikes in the floor.<br><br><strong>But remember:<br>You lure the enemy into your trap — try not to get caught in it yourself!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/3ee51c729e6cde16008ebba25056584d.poster.avif?t=1735721468\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/3ee51c729e6cde16008ebba25056584d.webm?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/3ee51c729e6cde16008ebba25056584d.mp4?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Is that it…? </strong><br><br><strong>Not really! The dungeon holds some helpful backups:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>weapon enhancers<br></li><li>throwable weapons<br></li><li>explosives<br></li><li>food<br></li><li>traps... </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/0281c7db491835f0eb6590757a73c893.poster.avif?t=1735721468\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/0281c7db491835f0eb6590757a73c893.webm?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/0281c7db491835f0eb6590757a73c893.mp4?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Or you could craft these items from found junk!</strong><br><br>Surely you can throw a stone at the enemy and give them a slight headache…<br>OR you could find another stone and make a bolas out of two. One throw — and the enemy is immobile!<br><br><strong>Hungry?</strong><br>Eat a carrot now — you restore 1 Health Point. <br>Mix the carrot with a chile pepper — 2 Health Points, a pinch of Fury bonus — and the delicious salad is done! <br><br><strong>Play around and combine!<br>Bon Appétit!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/fa53882d48152884ea7d997dc1cbbf06.poster.avif?t=1735721468\" width=600 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/fa53882d48152884ea7d997dc1cbbf06.webm?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/fa53882d48152884ea7d997dc1cbbf06.mp4?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Want to get the items immediately? </strong><br><br>You can build and upgrade 4 structures at your base:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>a workbench<br></li><li>an alchemy table<br></li><li>a field kitchen<br></li><li>and a garden  </li></ul><br>One structure = one item!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/644f88b87e64a7d88743fe780b4322e0.poster.avif?t=1735721468\" width=600 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/644f88b87e64a7d88743fe780b4322e0.webm?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/644f88b87e64a7d88743fe780b4322e0.mp4?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>So now you think you’re all armed and dangerous… <br>Don’t get loosey-goosey too soon — you might be cursed!</strong><br>Some enemies, traps, and magical items apply Curses to you — slow walking, no health restore, etc… <br><br><strong>But if there’s a Curse, there should be a Blessing!</strong><br>One Blessing token — one positive effect: electric feet, fire hands, armor enhancement, etc.<br>Combine the tokens from one set correctly together — get the best out of them!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/63fcd47110aa443df771f3e19c98a772.poster.avif?t=1735721468\" width=600 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/63fcd47110aa443df771f3e19c98a772.webm?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352470/extras/63fcd47110aa443df771f3e19c98a772.mp4?t=1735721468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Vile enemies, and ways to pin them down — going to do it alone or with a friend?..</strong><br><br><strong>It's up to you!</strong><br><br><strong>Ah yes… Almost forgot…</strong><br>The main characters are not some fluffy-wuffy wabbits — no — these are legit hares!",
